      "message": "\u003e Thanks for looking at this Braden.\n\u003e \n\u003e Mark, do you have any feelings on the align specs in our dbghelp.h copies? I\u0027m wondering if they should be 8 on x64 based on that being the natural alignment https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/cpp/align-cpp?view\u003dmsvc-160 and that there\u0027s nothing in the Windows SDK headers.\n\nWe froze everything at the alignment used on 32-bit platforms because anything else would be an interoperability nightmare, and I thought Microsoft did the same. But if they don’t, then we have a different interoperability nightmare.\n\nI’m getting out of here early to try to put 2020 behind me, so I won’t be able to test, but I’d suggest figuring out the right answer based on what MiniDumpWriteDump does.",
